title: "wickra-terminal"
abstract: >-
  A streaming trading terminal built on the Wickra core: one data-driven core
  exposed in ten languages, with a native TUI and a Web front-end as a selectable
  renderer. Panels emit view-models, so one core logic drives every front-end.
